sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Project Manager

participant UI as Resource Tagging UI
participant BFF as Execution BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant RMS as Resource Management Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}

PM->>UI: Open Resource Tagging worklist
UI->>BFF: Load projects in ResourceTagging state
BFF->>ORCH: Get resource tagging worklist
ORCH->>RMS: Fetch eligible projects
RMS->>READDB: Query project and resource tagging worklist
READDB-->>RMS: Project list
RMS-->>ORCH: Worklist response
ORCH-->>BFF: Aggregated response
BFF-->>UI: Show worklist with search and CTA